  <li id="comment-13064" class="comment even thread-even depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Mel</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2008/09/on-cue/#comment-13064"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2008-09-30T13:00:00-04:00">Tuesday, September 30, 2008 at 1:00 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Hey Molly&#8230;I&#8217;ve made a similar recipe that I learned from my boyfriends zia while visiting her in Italy.  Do add cheese!  As long as its the real parmigiano reggiano.  Or if you&#8217;re on a budget grana padano is a good substitute.</p>
    </div>

